MY VOICE
I've got that friendly young adult, millennial, cool-nerd, guy-next-door voice that's easy to listen and relate to. I'm consistently cast for 20s-30s-40s voice roles.

✔ Fast Turnaround (Often 24 Hours or Less)

✔ Commercials
